                            <note rend="inline" type="source">211.68/154: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Chargé in Greece</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Shantz</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-08-09T17:00:00-04:00">August 9, 1937—5
                                        p.m.</date></dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>34. Your 59, August 2, 2 p.m. You are authorized to sign protocol,
                                transmitting one of signed copies to Department.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi></signed></closer>
